var book = {
	"name": "1 Peter",
	"numChapters": 5,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Peter, an apostle of Jesus Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30376A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30376A\"></sup>To God’s elect,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30376B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30376B\"></sup> exiles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30376C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30376C\"></sup> scattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30376D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30376D\"></sup> throughout the provinces of Pontus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30376E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30376E\"></sup> Galatia,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30376F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30376F\"></sup> Cappadocia, Asia and Bithynia,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30376G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30376G\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>who have been chosen according to the foreknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30377H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30377H\"></sup> of God the Father, through the sanctifying work of the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30377I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30377I\"></sup> to be obedient<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30377J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30377J\"></sup> to Jesus Christ and sprinkled with his blood:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30377K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30377K\"></sup>Grace and peace be yours in abundance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30377L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30377L\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Praise be to the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30378M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30378M\"></sup> In his great mercy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30378N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30378N\"></sup> he has given us new birth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30378O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30378O\"></sup> into a living hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30378P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30378P\"></sup> through the resurrection of Jesus Christ from the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30378Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30378Q\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and into an inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30379R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30379R\"></sup> that can never perish, spoil or fade.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30379S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30379S\"></sup> This inheritance is kept in heaven for you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30379T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30379T\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>who through faith are shielded by God’s power<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30380U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30380U\"></sup> until the coming of the salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30380V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30380V\"></sup> that is ready to be revealed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30380W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30380W\"></sup> in the last time.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In all this you greatly rejoice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30381X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30381X\"></sup> though now for a little while<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30381Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30381Y\"></sup> you may have had to suffer grief in all kinds of trials.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30381Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30381Z\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>These have come so that the proven genuineness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30382AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30382AA\"></sup> of your faith—of greater worth than gold, which perishes even though refined by fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30382AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30382AB\"></sup>—may result in praise, glory and honor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30382AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30382AC\"></sup> when Jesus Christ is revealed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30382AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30382AD\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Though you have not seen him, you love him; and even though you do not see him now, you believe in him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30383AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30383AE\"></sup> and are filled with an inexpressible and glorious joy,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>for you are receiving the end result of your faith, the salvation of your souls.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30384AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30384AF\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Concerning this salvation, the prophets, who spoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30385AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30385AG\"></sup> of the grace that was to come to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30385AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30385AH\"></sup> searched intently and with the greatest care,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30385AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30385AI\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>trying to find out the time and circumstances to which the Spirit of Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30386AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30386AJ\"></sup> in them was pointing when he predicted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30386AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30386AK\"></sup> the sufferings of the Messiah and the glories that would follow.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It was revealed to them that they were not serving themselves but you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30387AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30387AL\"></sup> when they spoke of the things that have now been told you by those who have preached the gospel to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30387AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30387AM\"></sup> by the Holy Spirit sent from heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30387AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30387AN\"></sup> Even angels long to look into these things.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore, with minds that are alert and fully sober,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30388AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30388AO\"></sup> set your hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30388AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30388AP\"></sup> on the grace to be brought to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30388AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30388AQ\"></sup> when Jesus Christ is revealed at his coming.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30388AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30388AR\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As obedient<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30389AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30389AS\"></sup> children, do not conform<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30389AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30389AT\"></sup> to the evil desires you had when you lived in ignorance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30389AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30389AU\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But just as he who called you is holy, so be holy in all you do;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30390AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30390AV\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for it is written: “Be holy, because I am holy.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30391AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30391AW\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Since you call on a Father<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30392AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30392AX\"></sup> who judges each person’s work<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30392AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30392AY\"></sup> impartially,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30392AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30392AZ\"></sup> live out your time as foreigners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30392BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30392BA\"></sup> here in reverent fear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30392BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30392BB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For you know that it was not with perishable things such as silver or gold that you were redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30393BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30393BC\"></sup> from the empty way of life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30393BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30393BD\"></sup> handed down to you from your ancestors,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>but with the precious blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30394BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30394BE\"></sup> of Christ, a lamb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30394BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30394BF\"></sup> without blemish or defect.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30394BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30394BG\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He was chosen before the creation of the world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30395BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30395BH\"></sup> but was revealed in these last times<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30395BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30395BI\"></sup> for your sake.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Through him you believe in God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30396BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30396BJ\"></sup> who raised him from the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30396BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30396BK\"></sup> and glorified him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30396BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30396BL\"></sup> and so your faith and hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30396BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30396BM\"></sup> are in God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Now that you have purified<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30397BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30397BN\"></sup> yourselves by obeying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30397BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30397BO\"></sup> the truth so that you have sincere love for each other, love one another deeply,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30397BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30397BP\"></sup> from the heart.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For you have been born again,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30398BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30398BQ\"></sup> not of perishable seed, but of imperishable,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30398BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30398BR\"></sup> through the living and enduring word of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30398BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30398BS\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For,“All people are like grass,and all their glory is like the flowers of the field;the grass withers and the flowers fall,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>but the word of the Lord endures forever.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30400BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30400BT\"></sup>And this is the word that was preached to you."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Therefore, rid yourselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30401A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30401A\"></sup> of all malice and all deceit, hypocrisy, envy, and slander<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30401B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30401B\"></sup> of every kind.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Like newborn babies, crave pure spiritual milk,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30402C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30402C\"></sup> so that by it you may grow up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30402D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30402D\"></sup> in your salvation,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>now that you have tasted that the Lord is good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30403E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30403E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>As you come to him, the living Stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30404F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30404F\"></sup>—rejected by humans but chosen by God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30404G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30404G\"></sup> and precious to him—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>you also, like living stones, are being built<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30405H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30405H\"></sup> into a spiritual house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30405I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30405I\"></sup> to be a holy priesthood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30405J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30405J\"></sup> offering spiritual sacrifices acceptable to God through Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30405K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30405K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For in Scripture it says:“See, I lay a stone in Zion,a chosen and precious cornerstone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30406L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30406L\"></sup>and the one who trusts in himwill never be put to shame.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30406M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30406M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now to you who believe, this stone is precious. But to those who do not believe,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30407N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30407N\"></sup>“The stone the builders rejected<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30407O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30407O\"></sup>has become the cornerstone,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30407P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30407P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and,“A stone that causes people to stumbleand a rock that makes them fall.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30408Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30408Q\"></sup>They stumble because they disobey the message—which is also what they were destined for.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30408R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30408R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But you are a chosen people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30409S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30409S\"></sup> a royal priesthood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30409T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30409T\"></sup> a holy nation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30409U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30409U\"></sup> God’s special possession,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30409V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30409V\"></sup> that you may declare the praises of him who called you out of darkness into his wonderful light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30409W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30409W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Once you were not a people, but now you are the people of God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30410X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30410X\"></sup> once you had not received mercy, but now you have received mercy.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Dear friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30411Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30411Y\"></sup> I urge you, as foreigners and exiles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30411Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30411Z\"></sup> to abstain from sinful desires,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30411AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30411AA\"></sup> which wage war against your soul.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30411AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30411AB\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Live such good lives among the pagans that, though they accuse you of doing wrong, they may see your good deeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30412AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30412AC\"></sup> and glorify God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30412AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30412AD\"></sup> on the day he visits us.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Submit yourselves for the Lord’s sake to every human authority:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30413AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30413AE\"></sup> whether to the emperor, as the supreme authority,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>or to governors, who are sent by him to punish those who do wrong<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30414AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30414AF\"></sup> and to commend those who do right.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30414AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30414AG\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For it is God’s will<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30415AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30415AH\"></sup> that by doing good you should silence the ignorant talk of foolish people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30415AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30415AI\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Live as free people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30416AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30416AJ\"></sup> but do not use your freedom as a cover-up for evil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30416AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30416AK\"></sup> live as God’s slaves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30416AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30416AL\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Show proper respect to everyone, love the family of believers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30417AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30417AM\"></sup> fear God, honor the emperor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30417AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30417AN\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Slaves, in reverent fear of God submit yourselves to your masters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30418AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30418AO\"></sup> not only to those who are good and considerate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30418AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30418AP\"></sup> but also to those who are harsh.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For it is commendable if someone bears up under the pain of unjust suffering because they are conscious of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30419AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30419AQ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But how is it to your credit if you receive a beating for doing wrong and endure it? But if you suffer for doing good and you endure it, this is commendable before God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30420AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30420AR\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To this<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30421AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30421AS\"></sup> you were called,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30421AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30421AT\"></sup> because Christ suffered for you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30421AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30421AU\"></sup> leaving you an example,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30421AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30421AV\"></sup> that you should follow in his steps.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“He committed no sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30422AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30422AW\"></sup>and no deceit was found in his mouth.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30422AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30422AX\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When they hurled their insults at him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30423AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30423AY\"></sup> he did not retaliate; when he suffered, he made no threats.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30423AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30423AZ\"></sup> Instead, he entrusted himself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30423BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30423BA\"></sup> to him who judges justly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30423BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30423BB\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“He himself bore our sins”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30424BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30424BC\"></sup> in his body on the cross,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30424BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30424BD\"></sup> so that we might die to sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30424BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30424BE\"></sup> and live for righteousness; “by his wounds you have been healed.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30424BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30424BF\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For “you were like sheep going astray,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30425BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30425BG\"></sup> but now you have returned to the Shepherd<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30425BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30425BH\"></sup> and Overseer of your souls.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30425BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30425BI\"></sup>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Wives, in the same way submit yourselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30426A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30426A\"></sup> to your own husbands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30426B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30426B\"></sup> so that, if any of them do not believe the word, they may be won over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30426C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30426C\"></sup> without words by the behavior of their wives,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>when they see the purity and reverence of your lives.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Your beauty should not come from outward adornment, such as elaborate hairstyles and the wearing of gold jewelry or fine clothes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30428D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30428D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Rather, it should be that of your inner self,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30429E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30429E\"></sup> the unfading beauty of a gentle and quiet spirit, which is of great worth in God’s sight.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30429F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30429F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For this is the way the holy women of the past who put their hope in God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30430G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30430G\"></sup> used to adorn themselves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30430H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30430H\"></sup> They submitted themselves to their own husbands,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>like Sarah, who obeyed Abraham and called him her lord.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30431I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30431I\"></sup> You are her daughters if you do what is right and do not give way to fear.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Husbands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30432J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30432J\"></sup> in the same way be considerate as you live with your wives, and treat them with respect as the weaker partner and as heirs with you of the gracious gift of life, so that nothing will hinder your prayers.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Finally, all of you, be like-minded,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30433K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30433K\"></sup> be sympathetic, love one another,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30433L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30433L\"></sup> be compassionate and humble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30433M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30433M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do not repay evil with evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30434N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30434N\"></sup> or insult with insult.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30434O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30434O\"></sup> On the contrary, repay evil with blessing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30434P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30434P\"></sup> because to this<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30434Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30434Q\"></sup> you were called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30434R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30434R\"></sup> so that you may inherit a blessing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30434S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30434S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For,“Whoever would love lifeand see good daysmust keep their tongue from eviland their lips from deceitful speech.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They must turn from evil and do good;they must seek peace and pursue it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For the eyes of the Lord are on the righteousand his ears are attentive to their prayer,but the face of the Lord is against those who do evil.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30437T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30437T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Who is going to harm you if you are eager to do good?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30438U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30438U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But even if you should suffer for what is right, you are blessed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30439V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30439V\"></sup> “Do not fear their threats; do not be frightened.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30439W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30439W\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But in your hearts revere Christ as Lord. Always be prepared to give an answer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30440X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30440X\"></sup> to everyone who asks you to give the reason for the hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30440Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30440Y\"></sup> that you have. But do this with gentleness and respect,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>keeping a clear conscience,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30441Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30441Z\"></sup> so that those who speak maliciously against your good behavior in Christ may be ashamed of their slander.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30441AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30441AA\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For it is better, if it is God’s will,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30442AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30442AB\"></sup> to suffer for doing good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30442AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30442AC\"></sup> than for doing evil.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For Christ also suffered once<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30443AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30443AD\"></sup> for sins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30443AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30443AE\"></sup> the righteous for the unrighteous, to bring you to God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30443AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30443AF\"></sup> He was put to death in the body<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30443AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30443AG\"></sup> but made alive in the Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30443AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30443AH\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>After being made alive, he went and made proclamation to the imprisoned spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30444AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30444AI\"></sup>—",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>to those who were disobedient long ago when God waited patiently<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30445AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30445AJ\"></sup> in the days of Noah while the ark was being built.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30445AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30445AK\"></sup> In it only a few people, eight in all,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30445AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30445AL\"></sup> were saved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30445AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30445AM\"></sup> through water,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and this water symbolizes baptism that now saves you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30446AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30446AN\"></sup> also—not the removal of dirt from the body but the pledge of a clear conscience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30446AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30446AO\"></sup> toward God. It saves you by the resurrection of Jesus Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30446AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30446AP\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>who has gone into heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30447AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30447AQ\"></sup> and is at God’s right hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30447AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30447AR\"></sup>—with angels, authorities and powers in submission to him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30447AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30447AS\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Therefore, since Christ suffered in his body,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30448A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30448A\"></sup> arm yourselves also with the same attitude, because whoever suffers in the body is done with sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30448B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30448B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>As a result, they do not live the rest of their earthly lives for evil human desires,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30449C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30449C\"></sup> but rather for the will of God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For you have spent enough time in the past<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30450D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30450D\"></sup> doing what pagans choose to do—living in debauchery, lust, drunkenness, orgies, carousing and detestable idolatry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30450E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30450E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They are surprised that you do not join them in their reckless, wild living, and they heap abuse on you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30451F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30451F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But they will have to give account to him who is ready to judge the living and the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30452G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30452G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For this is the reason the gospel was preached even to those who are now dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30453H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30453H\"></sup> so that they might be judged according to human standards in regard to the body, but live according to God in regard to the spirit.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The end of all things is near.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30454I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30454I\"></sup> Therefore be alert and of sober mind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30454J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30454J\"></sup> so that you may pray.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Above all, love each other deeply,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30455K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30455K\"></sup> because love covers over a multitude of sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30455L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30455L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Offer hospitality<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30456M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30456M\"></sup> to one another without grumbling.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30456N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30456N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Each of you should use whatever gift you have received to serve others,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30457O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30457O\"></sup> as faithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30457P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30457P\"></sup> stewards of God’s grace in its various forms.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If anyone speaks, they should do so as one who speaks the very words of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30458Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30458Q\"></sup> If anyone serves, they should do so with the strength God provides,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30458R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30458R\"></sup> so that in all things God may be praised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30458S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30458S\"></sup> through Jesus Christ. To him be the glory and the power for ever and ever. Amen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30458T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30458T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Dear friends, do not be surprised at the fiery ordeal that has come on you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30459U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30459U\"></sup> to test you, as though something strange were happening to you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30460V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30460V\"></sup> inasmuch as you participate in the sufferings of Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30460W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30460W\"></sup> so that you may be overjoyed when his glory is revealed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30460X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30460X\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If you are insulted because of the name of Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30461Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30461Y\"></sup> you are blessed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30461Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30461Z\"></sup> for the Spirit of glory and of God rests on you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If you suffer, it should not be as a murderer or thief or any other kind of criminal, or even as a meddler.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>However, if you suffer as a Christian, do not be ashamed, but praise God that you bear that name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30463AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30463AA\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For it is time for judgment to begin with God’s household;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30464AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30464AB\"></sup> and if it begins with us, what will the outcome be for those who do not obey the gospel of God?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30464AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30464AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And,“If it is hard for the righteous to be saved,what will become of the ungodly and the sinner?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30465AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30465AD\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So then, those who suffer according to God’s will<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30466AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30466AE\"></sup> should commit themselves to their faithful Creator and continue to do good."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>To the elders among you, I appeal as a fellow elder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30467A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30467A\"></sup> and a witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30467B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30467B\"></sup> of Christ’s sufferings who also will share in the glory to be revealed:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30467C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30467C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Be shepherds of God’s flock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30468D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30468D\"></sup> that is under your care, watching over them—not because you must, but because you are willing, as God wants you to be;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30468E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30468E\"></sup> not pursuing dishonest gain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30468F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30468F\"></sup> but eager to serve;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>not lording it over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30469G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30469G\"></sup> those entrusted to you, but being examples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30469H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30469H\"></sup> to the flock.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And when the Chief Shepherd<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30470I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30470I\"></sup> appears, you will receive the crown of glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30470J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30470J\"></sup> that will never fade away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30470K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30470K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>In the same way, you who are younger, submit yourselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30471L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30471L\"></sup> to your elders. All of you, clothe yourselves with humility<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30471M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30471M\"></sup> toward one another, because,“God opposes the proudbut shows favor to the humble.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30471N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30471N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Humble yourselves, therefore, under God’s mighty hand, that he may lift you up in due time.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30472O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30472O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Cast all your anxiety on him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30473P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30473P\"></sup> because he cares for you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30473Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30473Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Be alert and of sober mind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30474R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30474R\"></sup> Your enemy the devil prowls around<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30474S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30474S\"></sup> like a roaring lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30474T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30474T\"></sup> looking for someone to devour.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Resist him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30475U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30475U\"></sup> standing firm in the faith,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30475V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30475V\"></sup> because you know that the family of believers throughout the world is undergoing the same kind of sufferings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30475W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30475W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the God of all grace, who called you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30476X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30476X\"></sup> to his eternal glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30476Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30476Y\"></sup> in Christ, after you have suffered a little while,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30476Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30476Z\"></sup> will himself restore you and make you strong,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30476AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30476AA\"></sup> firm and steadfast.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>To him be the power for ever and ever. Amen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30477AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30477AB\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>With the help of Silas,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30478AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30478AC\"></sup> whom I regard as a faithful brother, I have written to you briefly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30478AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30478AD\"></sup> encouraging you and testifying that this is the true grace of God. Stand fast in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30478AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30478AE\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>She who is in Babylon, chosen together with you, sends you her greetings, and so does my son Mark.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30479AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30479AF\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Greet one another with a kiss of love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30480AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30480AG\"></sup>Peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30480AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30480AH\"></sup> to all of you who are in Christ."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;